<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Commander" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Commander,</orth> 1) chief, leader: <bibl n="shak. luc 1387" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1387</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 4.1.67" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. IV, 1, 67</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 3.5.6" default="NO" valid="yes">All's III, 5, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.3.153" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 153</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.6.74" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 6, 74</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 4.1.97" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 97</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.3.48" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 3, 48</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.2.67" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 2, 67</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 1.3.55" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 3, 55</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 2.3.47" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 3, 47</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 4.2.48" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. IV, 2, 48</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 4.3.139" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 139</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 2.3.279" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 3, 279</bibl>.<lb />2) lord, master: <emph>invisible c.</emph> (Death) <bibl n="shak. ven 1004" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 1004</bibl>. <cit><quote>ay, my c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.167" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 167</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I was the world's c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.565" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 565</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>c. of this hot malicious day,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jn 2.314" default="NO" valid="yes">John II, 314</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>Saturnine, king and c. of our commonweal,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 1.247" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. I, 247</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>Lord of my life, c. of my thoughts,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 4.4.28" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 28</bibl></cit>.
